Escaping the chaos of fight-or-flight mode transformed my life, and I want to share the journey with you! 🌟 

Here are the 5 key steps that pulled me out of the stress abyss:

🚫 Save for later. 

1️⃣ Grounding with nature: Stripping off my shoes, taking long walks, and immersing myself in the world around me. Nature became my sanctuary, helping me find peace amidst the chaos.

2️⃣ Mindful Exercise: Whether it was pumping iron at the gym or embracing the serenity of a long walk or run, exercise became my ally. Listening to my body and giving it what it needed became my fitness mantra.

3️⃣ Cutting toxic ties: Setting boundaries was tough, but essential. Eliminating people who didn’t contribute positively to my life was a game-changer. It’s about surrounding yourself with those who uplift and support.

4️⃣ EFT Magic: Tapping into Emotional Freedom Techniques (EFT) worked wonders! By tapping on 7 meridian points, I rewired my mind, regulated emotions and manifested positivity. A technique I now teach in my coaching sessions!

5️⃣ Living for me: Putting myself first became my mantra. Doing things I loved and prioritizing my happiness allowed me to break free from living for others.
